Exploring | Dolomites, Italy

Here is @sandra.mode coming to join me after (or perhaps during) a snowstorm high in the Dolomites.

Tranquil | Lago di Braies, Italy

Just arrived back from a week shooting in Italy with my friends @sandra.mode, @erikhageman, @mumhad1ofthose and @descurran. The Dolomites are such a great area to explore.

This was taken during the last @f8workshops photography expedition to the Faroe Islands. We luckily have one ticket left for next month's workshop there with me, @zobolondon and @photojbartlett! Check the link in my bio for more details.

#f8workshops #f8faroeislands #lonelyplanet #canon_photos #beautifuldestinations #smugmug #guardiantravelsnaps

My own title cracks me up! I'm a genius. One of my fav locations in Northern Ireland and a pleasure to show @sandra.mode around.
